---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Cognit System"
  description="How Cognit System (a Zeabyte product) collects, uses and protects the personal information you share with us through cognitsystem.com — including enquiry and demo requests."
  path="/privacy"
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-cog-stone text-cog-slate">
    <!-- HERO (photographic) -->
    <section class="orbs relative isolate overflow-hidden">
      <img src="/images/hero-port-night.jpg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 h-full w-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-cog-ink/82"></div>
      <div class="dotgrid absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-40"></div>
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-5 pt-20 pb-20 text-center sm:px-8 sm:pt-28 hero-rise">
        <span class="chip mx-auto border border-white/15 text-slate-200">
          <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-cog-teal"></span> Your information, respected
        </span>
        <h1 class="mx-auto mt-7 max-w-3xl text-[2.6rem] font-extrabold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl">
          Privacy <span class="text-gradient-bright">Policy</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
          Plain English on what we collect when you contact us, why, and how we look
          after it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- BODY -->
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-20 sm:px-8">
      <article class="article">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-cog-slate/70">Last updated: 20 June 2026</p>

        <p>
          This Privacy Policy explains how <strong>Cognit System</strong> — a product of
          <strong>Zeabyte Limited</strong> (NZBN 9429052028748) — handles the personal
          information you give us through this website, <strong>cognitsystem.com</strong>.
          We keep it short and honest. If anything here is unclear, email us at
          <a href="mailto:contact@zeabyte.co.nz">contact@zeabyte.co.nz</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>What we collect</h2>
        <p>
          We only collect the information you choose to give us when you fill in our
          enquiry or demo-request form, or when you email us. That typically includes:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your name</li>
          <li>Your company or business name</li>
          <li>Your email address</li>
          <li>Your phone number</li>
          <li>The message or enquiry you send us</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do not ask for sensitive personal information through this website, and we
          don't sell your details to anyone.
        </p>

        <h2>How we use it</h2>
        <p>We use the information you give us to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Reply to your enquiry and arrange the demo you've asked for;</li>
          <li>Answer your questions and provide information about Cognit;</li>
          <li>Follow up about becoming a customer, and provide the service if you do;</li>
          <li>Keep a record of our correspondence with you.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We will not use your details for unrelated marketing without your consent, and
          every email we send you will give you a clear way to opt out.
        </p>

        <h2>Our lawful basis</h2>
        <p>
          We collect and use your information because you have asked us to get in touch
          (your consent and our legitimate interest in responding to you), and to take
          the steps you've requested before entering into a contract. We handle all
          personal information in line with the New Zealand Privacy Act 2020.
        </p>

        <h2>Storage &amp; security</h2>
        <p>
          Your information is stored securely and access is limited to the people who
          need it to respond to you or provide the service. We use trusted service
          providers and reasonable technical and organisational measures to protect your
          information against loss, misuse and unauthorised access. No system is ever
          completely secure, but we take protecting your information seriously.
        </p>

        <h2>Third parties</h2>
        <p>
          We use a small number of trusted service providers to run our business — for
          example, to deliver and store email, and to host this website. These providers
          only handle your information on our instructions and to provide their service to
          us. We do not sell, rent or trade your personal information to anyone.
        </p>

        <h2>Data retention</h2>
        <p>
          We keep your enquiry and contact details only for as long as we need them — to
          respond to you, to support an ongoing relationship, or as required by law. When
          we no longer need them, we securely delete or anonymise them.
        </p>

        <h2>Your rights</h2>
        <p>Under the New Zealand Privacy Act 2020, you can ask us to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Confirm what personal information we hold about you;</li>
          <li>Access a copy of that information;</li>
          <li>Correct anything that's wrong or out of date;</li>
          <li>Delete your information where we no longer need it;</li>
          <li>Stop contacting you.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To make any of these requests, just email
          <a href="mailto:contact@zeabyte.co.nz">contact@zeabyte.co.nz</a> and we'll sort
          it out.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy from time to time. When we do, we'll change the "last
          updated" date at the top of this page. Please check back occasionally so you're
          aware of any changes.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact us</h2>
        <p>
          For any privacy question or request, contact:<br />
          <strong>Cognit System</strong>, a product of Zeabyte Limited<br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:contact@zeabyte.co.nz">contact@zeabyte.co.nz</a><br />
          Phone: +64 22 169 1376
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
